Attributes.Name: Creation Date
Attributes.Note: The creation date of an object.  It is automatically assigned when an object is created, and can never be changed.

Attributes.Name: Object ID
Attributes.Note: This is the object ID, a globally-unique identifier for the object.  It is automatically assigned when an object is created, and can never be changed.

Attributes.Name: Subscription
Attributes.Note: A read-only reference to the subscription an object is associated with.

Attributes.Name: Workspace
Attributes.Note: A reference to the workspace an object is associated with.  This field can only be set during object creation.

Attributes.Name: Changesets
Attributes.Note: Changesets associated with this artifact.

Attributes.Name: Description
Attributes.Note: Artifact description, which is a rich-text field.

Attributes.Name: Discussion
Attributes.Note: The discussions for this artifact.

Attributes.Name: Display Color
Attributes.Note: Display color for artifacts

Attributes.Name: Formatted ID
Attributes.Note: The formatted ID for an object.  This is automatically assigned when an object is created and can never be changed.  In queries, only include the integer portion and omit the prefix.

Attributes.Name: Last Update Date
Attributes.Note: The last update date of an object.  It is automatically assigned when an object is created or updated.

Attributes.Name: Name
Attributes.Note: The name of the artifact

Attributes.Name: Notes
Attributes.Note: Artifact notes, which is a rich-text field.

Attributes.Name: Owner
Attributes.Note: Artifact owner, a reference to the user.

AllowedValues.StringValue: Transfer Zilla rock findings to Ecom

Attributes.Name: Project
Attributes.Note: The project this artifact is associated with.

Attributes.Name: Ready
Attributes.Note: Whether or not this Artifact is ready

Attributes.Name: Revision History
Attributes.Note: A reference to the revision history (read-only) of the artifact.

Attributes.Name: Tags
Attributes.Note: Tags for Artifact

Attributes.Name: Accepted Date
Attributes.Note: The date that this artifact's schedule state was set to accepted.  This is automatically set.

Attributes.Name: Affects Doc
Attributes.Note: Does this defect affect documentation?

Attributes.Name: Attachments
Attributes.Note: Attachments associated with this defect

Attributes.Name: Blocked
Attributes.Note: Flag to determine if this artifact is blocked

Attributes.Name: Blocked Reason
Attributes.Note: The reason this artifact is blocked

Attributes.Name: Blocker
Attributes.Note: The blocker blocking this defect

Attributes.Name: Closed Date
Attributes.Note: The date that this defect was closed.  This is automatically set when the defect is changed to the 'closed' state.

Attributes.Name: Duplicates
Attributes.Note: Other defects that are duplicates of this defect

Attributes.Name: Environment
Attributes.Note: Defect environment (see allowed values)

Attributes.Name: Fixed In Build
Attributes.Note: The build number that this defect is fixed in

Attributes.Name: Found In Build
Attributes.Note: The build number that this defect was found in

Attributes.Name: In Progress Date
Attributes.Note: The date this defect went in-progress.

Attributes.Name: Iteration
Attributes.Note: The iteration that this artifact is scheduled in

Attributes.Name: Opened Date
Attributes.Note: The date that this artifact's schedule state was set to open.  This is automatically set.

Attributes.Name: Package
Attributes.Note: The package that this defect is assigned to.

Attributes.Name: Plan Estimate
Attributes.Note: Plan estimate of this artifact

Attributes.Name: Priority
Attributes.Note: Priority of this defect

Attributes.Name: Rank
Attributes.Note: Schedule rank

Attributes.Name: Recycled
Attributes.Note: Moved to Recycle Bin

AllowedValues.StringValue: Old stuff in Prod Lines (Engineering) that's been released

Attributes.Name: Release
Attributes.Note: The release that this artifact is scheduled in

Attributes.Name: Release Note
Attributes.Note: Does this defect affect release notes?

Attributes.Name: Requirement
Attributes.Note: The requirement that this defect is regarding. Either Requirement or TestCase can be specified, but not both.

Attributes.Name: Resolution
Attributes.Note: Resolution of this defect

Attributes.Name: Salesforce Case ID
Attributes.Note: The Salesforce.com Case ID this defect is associated with

Attributes.Name: Salesforce Case Number
Attributes.Note: The Salesforce.com Case Number this defect is associated with

Attributes.Name: Schedule State
Attributes.Note: Schedule state

Attributes.Name: Severity
Attributes.Note: Severity of this defect

Attributes.Name: State
Attributes.Note: State of the defect

Attributes.Name: Submitted By
Attributes.Note: The user that submitted this defect

Attributes.Name: Target Build
Attributes.Note: Target build number for fixing this defect

Attributes.Name: Target Date
Attributes.Note: Target date for fixing this defect

Attributes.Name: Task Actual Total
Attributes.Note: Task actual total of this artifact

Attributes.Name: Task Estimate Total
Attributes.Note: Task estimate total of this artifact

Attributes.Name: Task Remaining Total
Attributes.Note: Task remaining total of this artifact

Attributes.Name: Task Status
Attributes.Note: The status of the Tasks associated with this artifact.

Attributes.Name: Tasks
Attributes.Note: Tasks associated with completing.

Attributes.Name: Test Case
Attributes.Note: The test case that this defect is regarding. Either Requirement or TestCase can be specified, but not both.

Attributes.Name: Test Case Result
Attributes.Note: The test case result that this defect is regarding.  The TCR must be a result of the test case of this defect.

Attributes.Name: Test Case Status
Attributes.Note: The status of the TestCases associated with this artifact.

Attributes.Name: Test Cases
Attributes.Note: The Test Cases associated with this defect.

Attributes.Name: Verified In Build
Attributes.Note: The build number that this defect is verified in
